        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer848957441" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12185267419083007242">Well, damn. There had better be a sequel for this book! Penguin, you can&apos;t just leave us hanging there!<br/><br/>The first few chapters are absolutely riveting (you can read an excerpt here, btw: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.mtv.com/news/2051414/exclusive-ember-in-the-ashes'>http://www.mtv.com/news/2051414/exclu...</a>), and the cruel, merciless world these characters inhabit is well drawn. The feel of this book reminded me of the Legend trilogy, actually, though I think <i>Ember</i> is more complex in plot, characters, and setting. It&apos;s fantasy that feels a bit dystopian, which is pretty inter</span>
  <span id="freeText12185267419083007242" style="display:none">Well, damn. There had better be a sequel for this book! Penguin, you can't just leave us hanging there!<br /><br />The first few chapters are absolutely riveting (you can read an excerpt here, btw: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.mtv.com/news/2051414/exclusive-ember-in-the-ashes">http://www.mtv.com/news/2051414/exclu...</a>), and the cruel, merciless world these characters inhabit is well drawn. The feel of this book reminded me of the Legend trilogy, actually, though I think <i>Ember</i> is more complex in plot, characters, and setting. It's fantasy that feels a bit dystopian, which is pretty interesting. <br /><br />I'm mulling over a couple of major points that I think could have made this book better <a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[one of which involves complicated romantic entanglements <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>, but overall I enjoyed this very much. Review to come.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12185267419083007242" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


